us - user: the user application occupys the CPU time
sy - system: the CPU time of kernel thread 
ni - nice: the CPU time of application whose nice has been modified
id - idle:
wa - IO wait: The CPU time which is used to wait the IO completed
hi - hardware interrupt: The CPU time to handle the hardware interrupt
si - software interrupt: 
st: 


