PID 	USER      	PR		  NI    VIRT    RES    SHR 	S 	 %CPU %MEM    	 TIME+		 COMMAND 


'h': help
'A': 全屏和交替模式切换，交替模式会显示四个窗口

1. Def (默认字段组)
2. Job (任务字段组)
3. Mem (内存字段组)
4. Usr (用户字节组)

'B': 粗字体显示
'd' or 's': set the time of flush
'l' switch load 
't' switch tasks
'm' switch memory
'R' reverse sort
'c' trigger command
'i' show idle tasks
'V' tree
'Z' change color
'z' swicth color
'x' or 'y': highlight the x and y axis
'u' the app of specific user
'n' the numer of app
'k' kill task
'r' resort the priority


Shell command option:
-c command
-d default time
-i: show idle task
-n number: just show iterator number
-p pid
-u user
-U uid
